		<title type="html"><![CDATA[First Public Working Draft: WebRTC Encoded Transform]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.w3.org/blog/news/archives/9258" />

		<id>https://www.w3.org/blog/news/?p=9258</id>
