		<title type="html"><![CDATA[Patent Advisory Group for Second Screen Working Group Launched]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.w3.org/blog/news/archives/9201" />

		<id>https://www.w3.org/blog/news/?p=9201</id>
		<updated>2021-08-26T08:45:52Z</updated>
		<published>2021-08-19T13:25:57Z</published>
		<category scheme="https://www.w3.org/blog/news" term="Uncategorized" />
		<summary type="html"><![CDATA[In accordance with the W3C Patent Policy, W3C has launched a Second Screen Working Group Patent Advisory Group (PAG) in response to disclosures related to a specification of the Second Screen Working Group; see the PAG charter. W3C launches a PAG to resolve issues in the event a patent has been disclosed that may be [&#8230;]]]></summary>

					<content type="html" xml:base="https://www.w3.org/blog/news/archives/9201"><![CDATA[<p>In accordance with the <a href="/Consortium/Patent-Policy-20200915/">W3C Patent Policy</a>, W3C
 has launched a <a href="/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/">Second Screen Working
 Group Patent Advisory Group (PAG)</a> in response to <a href="/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/#disclosures">disclosures</a>
 related to a specification of the Second Screen Working Group; see
 the <a href="/2021/08/secondscreen-pag/charter.html">PAG charter</a>. W3C <a href="/Consortium/Patent-Policy-20200915/#sec-Exception">launches a
 PAG</a> to resolve issues in the event a patent has been disclosed
 that may be essential, but is not available under the <a href="/Consortium/Patent-Policy-20200915/#def-RF">W3C Royalty-Free
 licensing requirements</a>. Public comments regarding these
 disclosures may be sent to public-secondscreen-pag@w3.org (<a href="https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-secondscreen-pag/">public
 archive</a>). Learn more about <a href="/Consortium/Patent-Policy-20200915/#sec-Exception">Patent
 Advisory Groups</a>.</p>
]]></content>
		
